title: Sense of Place: Produce shopping for musical instruments in Vienna, Austria
description: Vienna is a city where the streets are alive with the sounds of violins, pianos, clarinets and ... vegetables!? A member of the city's Vegetable Orchestra takes us shopping at a local market for instruments.
